Generic single-database configuration.

flask本来没有migrate同步数据库的迁移操作, 用Flask-Migrate进行扩展之后可以用脚本的形式进行数据库的同步而不用code

flask: migrate == django: makemigrations, 
flask: upgrade == django: migrate,
flask: downgrade
flask: history

flask中的数据库命令: e.g.

python author_book.py db init
python author_book.py db migrate
python author_book.py db upgrade
python author_book.py db hostory
python author_book.py db downgrade
